String[] splits = str.split("[^a-z]");
this regex will split all by words only

[^a-z]

Example
countYZ("day yak") → 1	1	OK
countYZ("day:yak") → 1	1	OK
countYZ("!!day--yaz!!") → 2	2	OK
countYZ("DAY abc XYZ") → 2	2	OK
countYZ("y2bz") → 2	2	OK
countYZ("zxyx") → 0	0	OK
============================================